---
title: Grilled Beef Rump & Chilli-Crushed Potato with Blackened Eggplant Salad
description: Do you hear that? Your grill is calling your name again; it’s time for another epic barbecue feast! Tonight we’ve got a perfectly tender beef rump steak, served alongside crushed chilli-garlic potatoes. The salad is a real crowd-pleaser, with grilled eggplant and charred onion tossed through fresh salad leaves.Grab a fork and dig in!
